      "span_text": "To rigorously compare the ability of homologous DCEs to rescue DC bristle formation in D. melanogaster hosts, we took advantage of Df(1)91B, a 45-kilobase (kb) deletion that removes ac and the DCE, but leaves sc and most other regulatory elements intact  .",
